Run ADE review phases (Review + Verify + Documentation) for: $ARGUMENTS

1. Phase 6 — REVIEW: 3-lens parallel review of the diff:
   - Logic: errors, edge cases, null handling, race conditions
   - Conventions: project patterns, naming, structure
   - Security: OWASP top 10, injection, auth, secrets
   Classify: HIGH (blocking), MEDIUM (fix before merge), LOW (advisory)
2. Phase 7 — VERIFY: Live verification with evidence
   Verify acceptance criteria, capture screenshots/logs as evidence
3. Phase 8 — DOCUMENTATION: Update affected project docs

Report: APPROVED, MINOR_FIXES (with details), or MAJOR_ISSUES (escalate).
